name: Ai20x.ai
description: Ai20x is a decentralized finance protocol designed to create a fair and sustainable ecosystem for users. The protocol operates with community governance through a decentralized autonomous organization, allowing participants to vote on upgrades and key decisions. Ai20x integrates transparent reward mechanics to ensure that contributors and participants are treated equally, while also including mechanisms to mitigate volatility in its token economy. Its primary purpose is to align long term growth with fairness, giving users both utility and governance within a decentralized framework.
